{"root":{"data":{"text":"微波光子成像干扰一体化技术研究"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmyp0tfqfn4s","created":1531797858298,"text":"研究背景和意义","layout_right_offset":{"x":29,"y":0}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmyp15m8zmog","created":1531797884814,"text":"研究背景","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#92d050"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyy3hxxpm2o","created":1773129915403,"text":"军用领域"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyxqhw1j94w","created":1773128896555,"text":"现代战争中，无人机的广泛应用给雷达探测带来了新的挑战。"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyxvi6n2v40","created":1773129289016,"text":"无人机的雷达散射截面积远远小于舰船坦克等，大大提高了雷达识别无人机的难度。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgyxvulti29s","created":1773129316056,"text":"无人机往往数量繁多，还采用集群技术协同作战，如果想要精准探测不同的敌方目标，这就对于雷达分辨率提出了很高的要求。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgyxwh0757gg","created":1773129364814,"text":"雷达作为敌方攻击的重要目标，也需要具有一定的自保能力。"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyy4ppgombk","created":1773130010669,"text":"现代战场上敌方往往采用无人机饱和攻击消耗拦截系统的弹药，然后在空窗期发射导弹摧毁雷达。如果能识别干扰无人机只针对导弹进行拦截，就可以显著降低拦截系统的压力"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgyyqgatmhvk","created":1773131714205,"text":"现代战争雷达通信等设备的高频化宽带化"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyyslt4sb28","created":1773131882924,"text":"需要"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgyy3fxmim0w","created":1773129911031,"text":"民用领域"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyy3qzuyhog","created":1773129935111,"text":"无人机黑飞问题"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyybfuxms5c","created":1773130537782,"text":"无人机由于体型较小、可以低空起飞等原因，其监管存在较大难度。近些年来常常发生无人机在未经申请和授权的情况下黑飞进入机场或重要设施建筑的，不仅可能造成重大公共安全隐患，还可能导致重要信息泄漏。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgyy3w6xqj9c","created":1773129946423,"text":"无人机反制"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyybqxylzpc","created":1773130561909,"text":"需要既能够对无人机进行精准探测，又能够对其进行有效干扰的探测干扰一体化系统，从而实现有效的无人机反制。"},"children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgyygn6e0npc","created":1773130945533,"text":"探测干扰一体化的研究意义","layout":null,"background":"#92d050"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyyhk0uo934","created":1773131017032,"text":"节约资源，减轻作战平台负担","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyygy8sbl6o","created":1773130969622,"text":"如果需要额外配备干扰机和假目标靶标等来提高其生存能力，不仅加剧了作战平台的负担，也在一定程度上限制了其灵活性和机动性。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgyyi4oe7qww","created":1773131061991,"text":"减少设备种类和电磁兼容问题"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyymwe2pdkw","created":1773131435773,"text":"传统雷达多只承担单一任务，不仅使得设备种类繁多、使用不便还可能带来电磁兼容问题"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgyyhpnev4e8","created":1773131029280,"text":"多功能集成应对复杂战场环境"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyz27mbimf4","created":1773132635679,"text":"通过微波光子雷达成像干扰一体化设计，微波光子雷达探测得到的高分辨率成像结果可以用于判断敌方目标的位置、数量和类型等，从而可以根据不同情况选择不同的应对方式以应对复杂的战场环境"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp16beu2w4","created":1531797886335,"text":"国内外研究现状","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#92d050"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyy1vdqfmdc","created":1773129787928,"text":"电域"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyydbwomrr4","created":1773130685909,"text":"由于电子瓶颈的限制，传统电子学难以实现对于宽带信号的产生、处理和控制，因而使得雷达分辨率也有所受限。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgyysu45l2io","created":1773131901005,"text":"传统电子干扰技术实现"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyyt8x01mv4","created":1773131933224,"text":"DRFM（数字射频存储器）"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyyu543wlxc","created":1773132003311,"text":"典型的DRFM结构一般包含两个频率转换模块、本地振荡器（LO）、模数转换器（A\\D）、存储模块、数模转换器（D\\A）及控制器。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgyyii44k2yo","created":1773131091240,"text":"随着现代战争雷达通信等设备的高频化宽带化，这就对传统基于A\\D的DRFM提出了极高的采样速度要求，同时传统射频器件的工作带宽范围有限，使得数字射频储存器的工作频段受到极大限制。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgyxrcuisruo","created":1773128963943,"text":"得益于集成电路和相控阵等的发展等，传统电域探测干扰一体化程度高。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgyy1u22k2yo","created":1773129785046,"text":"微波光子"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyy2myyd6v4","created":1773129847985,"text":"基于微波光子技术我们可以同时实现高频宽带信号的高保真存储和高响应速度。"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dgyyizikf6yo","created":1773131129119,"text":"其一体化程度较低，多只承担单一探测或干扰功能。"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp16p7fl4o","created":1531797887169,"text":"微波光子技术的优势","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#92d050","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyz0i3kibk0","created":1773132501761,"text":"宽工作频段和瞬时带宽","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyxuynlbq4g","created":1773129246506,"text":"能够实现高分辨率雷达成像","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyy00vufzls","created":1773129643179,"text":"微波光子技术能够实现传统雷达复杂甚至难以实现的宽带微波信号处理与传输，极大提高了雷达系统的距离分辨率，带来了雷达体制新的变革。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgyy11p18wsg","created":1773129723308,"text":"能够实现高频宽带的干扰"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyy6aooksg0","created":1773130134699,"text":"基于微波光子技术的干扰信号产生能够解决数字射频存储器由于工作频段和瞬时带宽受限无法针对敌方雷达产生有效干扰的问题，有效提高雷达的生存能力。"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgyz1ax512ps","created":1773132564499,"text":"具有良好的可调谐性和抗电磁干扰特性"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dgyz1x1ska9s","created":1773132612670,"text":"可以灵活调谐其工作频段以适应不同的作战场景以及兼容干扰机和雷达工作时不同工作频段和带宽。"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dgyz3n0xfif4","created":1773132747578,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp0vi3wjs4","created":1531797862795,"text":"研究内容","layout_right_offset":{"x":29,"y":0}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmyp17ohlswk","created":1531797889303,"text":"1. 按区域","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#dbe5f1"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp18cjbegw","created":1531797890757,"text":"2. 按时间","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#dbe5f1"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp18qmdhs8","created":1531797891608,"text":"3. 按活动","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#dbe5f1"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp28g7gco4","created":1531797969343,"text":"4. 按重点","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#dbe5f1"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp0w7fnc0k","created":1531797864327,"text":"3. 亮点与不足","layout_right_offset":{"x":47,"y":0}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmyp19f2yo84","created":1531797893087,"text":"1. 工作亮点","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#92d050"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp19rtkeo8","created":1531797893858,"text":"2. 工作不足","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#92d050"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp0wnpf808","created":1531797865311,"text":"4. 阶段工作规划","layout_right_offset":{"x":29,"y":0}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmyp1apwzq8k","created":1531797895919,"text":"1. 按区域","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#f79646"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp1b1h3z4g","created":1531797896618,"text":"2. 按时间","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#f79646"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp1bd2qds8","created":1531797897320,"text":"3. 按活动","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#f79646"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp1brn0xcs","created":1531797898200,"text":"4. 按重点","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#f79646"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp0xg6s1s0","created":1531797867033,"text":"5. 改进建议","layout_right_offset":{"x":61,"y":0}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"bmyp1ccip1s8","created":1531797899463,"text":"1. 对公司","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#92d050"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"bmyp1d52ua04","created":1531797901190,"text":"2. 对部门","layout_right_offset":{"x":33,"y":0},"background":"#92d050"},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"right","theme":"fresh-red-compat","version":"1.4.43"}